The paper presents a new dataset for object detection on images, which is a common task in computer vision (cs.CV). The authors also provide their trained models as a benchmark, which suggests that they used machine learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI). The dataset could also be used for information retrieval (cs.IR) or multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
